title: UFYB 17: What Creates Your Personality
itunes:title: What Creates Your Personality
description:
Tune in to get your mind blow as I share my own personality theory that will challenge everything you think you know about the "type" of person you are... beginning with the question, "What if you don't have a personality at all?"

Get full show notes and more information here:  https://unfckyourbrain.com/17
